list.abstract: farmer（英 [ˈfɑːmə]，美 [ˈfɑːrmər]），英语单词，作名词为农场主；农民；包税人。例句为：The farmer bought the well happily.（农夫高兴地买下了这口井。） 近义词有peasant。

yingyinNormal.en: You can be a farmer, Rick. You can't just be a farmer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以当农民，瑞克，但不能只是个农民。

yingyinNormal.en: You're from Bunnyburrow, is that what you said? So how about a carrot farmer? That sound about right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是兔窝镇的，对吧？种胡萝卜的农民？听着不错吧？

yingyinNormal.en: But just outside St Albans, farmer Howard Roberts is a part of one such rare partnership that survives to this day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在圣奥尔本斯 农民霍华德 罗伯特就是今天幸存的这种罕见关系的一部分。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh my dear, where shall I start? Suppose the farmer talks? Suppose you're seen visiting his home, which I presume is the idea?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊，我该从何说起？如果农民开始议论纷纷呢？假如你被看到去他家，我想你就是这么打算的吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Which is what I've made for Howard the farmer, and Justin the miller.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这也是我为霍华德，贾斯汀做的。

yingyinNormal.en: This is California's central valley,and my guide is farmer Ted Sheeley.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里是加利福尼亚的中央山谷，我的向导是农场主泰德·舍利。

yingyinNormal.en: These are onion fields in Central California. Remember farmer Ted Sheeley?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些是加州中部的洋葱田。还记得农场主泰德·舍利吗?

yingyinNormal.en: How did the visit go? Well, George wants to be a pig farmer when he grows up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 农场之行怎么样？乔治长大后要做猪倌。

yingyinNormal.en: As for our Kansas farmer, Greg Stone, his corn-growing operation is under attack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而我们堪萨斯的农场主，格雷格斯通，他的玉米种植工程正在受到攻击。

yingyinNormal.en: But you haven't said what you think. Which side are you on? The farmer's, of course.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还没说你的看法呢,你支持哪一边?当然是佃户啦。

yingyinNormal.en: So, you're a practical farmer, as well as a theoretician. Not sure I was expecting that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看来你不仅懂农业理论，还会农活儿，这我可没料到。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you sure this is the right place, Daddy Pig? It just looks like a farmer's field to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你确定我们找对地方了吗，猪爸爸？我怎么觉得这里是一片土豆田。

yingyinNormal.en: Isn't my client the only farmer in Kane who doesn't use your seeds? Yes, I think that's right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的委托人是否是凯恩县唯一不用你种子的农场主？是，我想是这样。

yingyinNormal.en: Marie Audet is a second-generation dairy farmer who doesn't let anything go to waste on her farm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛丽·奥迪特是第二代奶农，她不允许她的农场有任何浪费。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe someday, I might like to be a... Zoo keeper? No. Pet shop boy? No. Farmer with chickies? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许有一天，我会成为一个……动物园管理员？不。宠物店店员？不。养鸡的农场主？不。

yingyinNormal.en: I have a champion. Do you know Fang Zhen of the Red Lotus Society? By reputation. A peasant farmer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有王牌，你有没有听说过红莲教的方正？略有耳闻，他是个农夫。

yingyinNormal.en: What? How? There's a tenant farmer, whose family has been at Downton for years. I'm sure he can be trusted.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？怎么做？有个佃户，他一家在唐顿生活了多年，我们能信任他。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the point? The other day she laughed for an hour at a cup. Just a cup with a picture of Elmo on it, dressed as a farmer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 重点在哪里？那天他对著杯子大笑一个多小时。只是一个普通杯子上面有阿母的农夫图案。

yingyinNormal.en: If this is working so well for you, how come everyone's not doing this? Well, it takes more than just the dairy farmer to get this done.
yingyinNormal.zh: 若这个对你来说效果这么好，为什么大家不效仿呢? 呃,这不仅仅是靠奶农就能搞定的。

yingyinNormal.en: Did the electricity go out? I don't know what you mean by "electricity," Ma'am. I am just a farmer boy living in a little house on the prairie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 停电了吗？女士，我不知道你说的"电"是什么。我只是一个住在草原小屋里的务农男孩。
